comments: Johnson (SAS) is moving alongside Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Beasley (MIL) lowers his arm and initiates contact to Johnson's (SAS) left arm, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Sochan (SAS) moves alongside Lillard's (MIL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Wembanyama (SAS) blocks the shot attempt when the ball is on its upward flight towards the basket and before it reaches its apex.
Lopez (MIL) legally contests Wembanyama's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Johnson's (SAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jones (SAS) does not establish himself in Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and initiates illegal contact to his lower body during his dunk.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) does not release his free throw attempt within ten seconds.
Wembanyama (SAS) establishes himself in Beasley's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Jones' (SAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Wembanyama (SAS) cleanly blocks Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shot attempt at the rim.
Johnson (SAS) dislodges Connaughton (MIL) from his rebounding position.
Wembanyama (SAS) does not establish himself out of bounds before releasing the throw-in to his teammate.
